---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { Code } from 'astro:components';


const metadata = {
  title: 'Documentation',
};

const apiServer = 'https://api.mamay.ai';
const apiModel = 'mamaylm-gemma-3-27b-fp8';
const apiAccessHref = 'mailto:chat.mamay@insait.ai?subject=API%20Access';

const hfModel = 'INSAIT-Institute/MamayLM-Gemma-3-27B-IT-v2.0';
const hfModel12b = 'INSAIT-Institute/MamayLM-Gemma-3-12B-IT-v2.0';
const hfModelUrl = `https://huggingface.co/${hfModel}`;
const hfModel12bUrl = `https://huggingface.co/${hfModel12b}`;

const proseClasses = 'prose prose-md lg:prose-xl dark:prose-invert dark:prose-headings:text-slate-300 prose-headings:font-heading prose-headings:leading-tighter prose-headings:tracking-tighter prose-headings:font-bold prose-a:text-primary dark:prose-a:text-blue-400 prose-img:rounded-md prose-img:shadow-lg prose-headings:scroll-mt-[180px] prose-li:my-0 prose-code:before:content-none prose-code:after:content-none prose-h2:border-t prose-h2:border-gray-200 prose-h2:dark:border-slate-700 prose-h2:pt-8 prose-h2:mt-12 prose-h2:text-2xl prose-h2:lg:text-3xl prose-h3:text-lg prose-h3:lg:text-xl prose-h3:text-muted prose-h3:dark:text-slate-400';
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="py-8 sm:py-16 lg:py-20 mx-auto">

    <!-- EN -->
    <div data-lang-en style="display:none">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter font-heading dark:text-gray-200">Documentation</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-muted dark:text-slate-400">Two ways to use MamayLM: call our <a href="#api" class="text-primary underline">hosted API</a>, or <a href="#self-hosting" class="text-primary underline">run the open models yourself</a> with HuggingFace or vLLM.</p>

        <nav class="mt-6 space-y-3">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary mr-1">Hosted API</span>
            <a href="#getting-started" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Getting Started</a>
            <a href="#chat-completions" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Chat</a>
            <a href="#streaming" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Streaming</a>
            <a href="#tool-calling" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Tool Calling</a>
            <a href="#vision" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Vision</a>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary mr-1">Run it yourself</span>
            <a href="#transformers" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Transformers</a>
            <a href="#vllm" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">vLLM</a>
            <a href="#model-info" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Model Info</a>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class={"mx-auto px-6 sm:px-6 max-w-3xl " + proseClasses}>

        <div id="api" class="not-prose mb-8 scroll-mt-[180px]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary">Hosted API</span>
            <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-slate-700"></span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted dark:text-slate-400 m-0">Call MamayLM over an OpenAI-compatible API — no infrastructure to manage.</p>
          <div class="mt-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300">
            Don't have an API key? <a href={apiAccessHref} class="font-semibold underline hover:text-gray-900 dark:hover:text-slate-100">Request access</a> and your key will be provisioned.
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="getting-started" class="!border-t-0 !mt-4 !pt-0">Getting Started</h2>
        <p>The MamayLM API is fully compatible with the <strong>OpenAI SDK</strong>. Any library or tool that supports the OpenAI Chat Completions API works with MamayLM.</p>

        <table>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td><strong>Endpoint</strong></td><td><code>{apiServer}/v1</code></td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Model</strong></td><td><code>{apiModel}</code></td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Auth</strong></td><td><code>Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY</code></td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Context</strong></td><td>Up to 65,536 tokens</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Quantization</strong></td><td>FP8 dynamic (same quality, 2x faster)</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <p>Install the OpenAI Python SDK:</p>
        <Code code="pip install openai" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />

        <h2 id="chat-completions">Chat Completions</h2>

        <h3>Python</h3>
        <Code code={`from openai import OpenAI

client = OpenAI(
    base_url="${apiServer}/v1",
    api_key="YOUR_API_KEY",
)

response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="${apiModel}",
    messages=[
        {"role": "system", "content": "You are a helpful assistant."},
        {"role": "user", "content": "Поясни простими словами, як утворюється веселка."}
    ],
    max_tokens=16384,
    temperature=0.2,
)
print(response.choices[0].message.content)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>curl</h3>
        <Code code={`curl -X POST ${apiServer}/v1/chat/completions \\
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \\
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \\
  -d '{
    "model": "${apiModel}",
    "messages": [
      {"role": "user", "content": "Поясни простими словами, як утворюється веселка."}
    ],
    "max_tokens": 16384,
    "temperature": 0.2
  }'`} lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />

        <h2 id="streaming">Streaming</h2>
        <p>Set <code>stream=True</code> to receive tokens as they are generated:</p>
        <Code code={`stream = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="${apiModel}",
    messages=[
        {"role": "user", "content": "Поясни простими словами, як утворюється веселка."}
    ],
    max_tokens=1024,
    stream=True,
)

for chunk in stream:
    delta = chunk.choices[0].delta
    if delta.content:
        print(delta.content, end="", flush=True)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h2 id="tool-calling">Tool Calling</h2>
        <p>MamayLM supports OpenAI-compatible tool calling. Define tools as JSON schemas, and the model will decide when to call them.</p>

        <h3>1. Define tools and send request</h3>
        <Code code={`tools = [
    {
        "type": "function",
        "function": {
            "name": "get_weather",
            "description": "Get the current weather for a city",
            "parameters": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "city": {"type": "string", "description": "City name"},
                    "unit": {"type": "string", "enum": ["celsius", "fahrenheit"]}
                },
                "required": ["city"]
            }
        }
    }
]

response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="${apiModel}",
    messages=[
        {"role": "user", "content": "What's the weather in Kyiv?"}
    ],
    tools=tools,
    tool_choice="auto",
)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>2. Check for tool calls</h3>
        <Code code={`message = response.choices[0].message

if message.tool_calls:
    for tool_call in message.tool_calls:
        print(f"Function: {tool_call.function.name}")
        print(f"Arguments: {tool_call.function.arguments}")
else:
    print(message.content)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>3. Send tool results back</h3>
        <Code code={`import json

# After calling your function with the model's arguments:
tool_result = {"temperature": 22, "unit": "celsius", "condition": "sunny"}

response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="${apiModel}",
    messages=[
        {"role": "user", "content": "What's the weather in Kyiv?"},
        message,  # the assistant message with tool_calls
        {
            "role": "tool",
            "tool_call_id": message.tool_calls[0].id,
            "content": json.dumps(tool_result),
        }
    ],
    tools=tools,
)
print(response.choices[0].message.content)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <p><strong>Supported <code>tool_choice</code> values:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li><code>"auto"</code> &mdash; model decides whether to call a tool (default)</li>
          <li><code>"required"</code> &mdash; model must call at least one tool</li>
          <li><code>"none"</code> &mdash; tool calling disabled for this request</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="vision">Vision</h2>
        <p>MamayLM v2.0 is multimodal and can understand images. Send images as base64 data URLs.</p>

        <h3>Base64 image</h3>
        <Code code={`import base64

with open("photo.jpg", "rb") as f:
    b64 = base64.b64encode(f.read()).decode()

response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="${apiModel}",
    messages=[
        {
            "role": "user",
            "content": [
                {"type": "text", "text": "Describe this image."},
                {
                    "type": "image_url",
                    "image_url": {"url": f"data:image/jpeg;base64,{b64}"}
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
    max_tokens=1024,
)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <div id="self-hosting" class="not-prose mt-16 mb-8 scroll-mt-[180px]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary">Run it yourself</span>
            <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-slate-700"></span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted dark:text-slate-400 m-0">MamayLM v2.0 is open — run the 12B or 27B models locally with HuggingFace Transformers or serve them with vLLM. No API key required.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 id="transformers" class="!border-t-0 !mt-4 !pt-0">Run with HuggingFace Transformers</h2>
        <p>MamayLM v2.0 is available on HuggingFace in <strong>27B</strong> (<a href={hfModelUrl}>{hfModel}</a>) and <strong>12B</strong> (<a href={hfModel12bUrl}>{hfModel12b}</a>) sizes. It is a Gemma 3 model, so load it with <code>Gemma3ForConditionalGeneration</code> and <code>AutoProcessor</code>.</p>

        <Code code="pip install -U transformers accelerate torch" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>Text generation</h3>
        <Code code={`from transformers import AutoProcessor, Gemma3ForConditionalGeneration
import torch

model_id = "${hfModel}"

processor = AutoProcessor.from_pretrained(model_id)
model = Gemma3ForConditionalGeneration.from_pretrained(
    model_id, device_map="auto"
).eval()

messages = [
    {
        "role": "user",
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Explain in simple terms how a rainbow forms."}],
    },
]

inputs = processor.apply_chat_template(
    messages, add_generation_prompt=True, tokenize=True,
    return_dict=True, return_tensors="pt"
).to(model.device, dtype=torch.bfloat16)

input_len = inputs["input_ids"].shape[-1]

with torch.inference_mode():
    generation = model.generate(**inputs, max_new_tokens=512, do_sample=True, temperature=0.2)
    generation = generation[0][input_len:]

print(processor.decode(generation, skip_special_tokens=True))`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>With an image</h3>
        <Code code={`messages = [
    {
        "role": "user",
        "content": [
            {"type": "image", "image": "https://huggingface.co/datasets/huggingface/documentation-images/resolve/main/bee.jpg"},
            {"type": "text", "text": "Describe what you see in the image."},
        ],
    },
]

inputs = processor.apply_chat_template(
    messages, add_generation_prompt=True, tokenize=True,
    return_dict=True, return_tensors="pt"
).to(model.device, dtype=torch.bfloat16)

input_len = inputs["input_ids"].shape[-1]

with torch.inference_mode():
    generation = model.generate(**inputs, max_new_tokens=512, do_sample=True, temperature=0.2)
    generation = generation[0][input_len:]

print(processor.decode(generation, skip_special_tokens=True))`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h2 id="vllm">Run with vLLM</h2>
        <p>vLLM gives you fast batched inference and an OpenAI-compatible server for self-hosting.</p>

        <Code code="pip install vllm" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>Python</h3>
        <Code code={`from vllm import LLM, SamplingParams

llm = LLM(model="${hfModel}")
params = SamplingParams(max_tokens=512, temperature=0.2)

messages = [
    {
        "role": "user",
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Explain in simple terms how a rainbow forms."}],
    },
]

outputs = llm.chat(messages, sampling_params=params)
print(outputs[0].outputs[0].text)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>OpenAI-compatible server</h3>
        <Code code={`vllm serve ${hfModel}`} lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
        <p>This exposes an OpenAI-compatible endpoint at <code>http://localhost:8000/v1</code>. Query it exactly like the <a href="#chat-completions">Chat Completions</a> examples above — just point <code>base_url</code> there.</p>

        <h3>FP8 for faster inference</h3>
        <p><strong>Do not</strong> use vLLM's on-the-fly <code>quantization="fp8"</code> flag with the base model — it silently quantizes the vision tower and multi-modal projector, producing garbage outputs on image inputs. For ~2× memory reduction with vision preserved, serve the FP8 dynamic variant instead:</p>
        <Code code={`vllm serve ${hfModel}-FP8-dynamic`} lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />

        <h2 id="model-info">Model Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://huggingface.co/INSAIT-Institute/MamayLM-Gemma-3-27B-IT-v2.0">MamayLM-Gemma-3-27B-IT</a> (based on <a href="https://huggingface.co/google/gemma-3-27b-it">gemma-3-27b-it</a>)</li>
          <li>FP8 dynamic quantization &mdash; uses about half the memory for weights compared to BF16, with minimal quality loss</li>
          <li>65,536 tokens context window (the base model supports up to 131,072)</li>
          <li><strong>Capabilities:</strong>
            <ul class="list-['◦']">
              <li>Text generation</li>
              <li>Instruction following</li>
              <li>Tool calling</li>
              <li>Vision (image understanding)</li>
              <li>Multi-turn conversations</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Read more about the model on the</strong> <a href="/blog/mamaylm-v2-release-en">MamayLM v2.0 blog</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="notes">Notes</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>The API is OpenAI-compatible. Any SDK or framework that supports OpenAI (LangChain, LlamaIndex, etc.) works with MamayLM by changing <code>base_url</code> and <code>api_key</code>.</li>
          <li>To request API access, write to <a href={apiAccessHref}>chat.mamay@insait.ai</a>.</li>
          <li>To run the model locally, see the <a href="https://huggingface.co/INSAIT-Institute/MamayLM-Gemma-3-27B-IT-v2.0">HuggingFace model card</a>.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- UK -->
    <div data-lang-uk>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter font-heading dark:text-gray-200">Документація</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-muted dark:text-slate-400">Два способи використовувати MamayLM: через наш <a href="#api-uk" class="text-primary underline">hosted API</a> або <a href="#self-hosting-uk" class="text-primary underline">запустивши відкриті моделі самостійно</a> за допомогою HuggingFace чи vLLM.</p>

        <nav class="mt-6 space-y-3">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary mr-1">Hosted API</span>
            <a href="#getting-started-uk" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Початок</a>
            <a href="#chat-completions-uk" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Чат</a>
            <a href="#streaming-uk" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Стрімінг</a>
            <a href="#tool-calling-uk" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Функції</a>
            <a href="#vision-uk" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Зображення</a>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary mr-1">Запустити самостійно</span>
            <a href="#transformers-uk" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Transformers</a>
            <a href="#vllm-uk" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">vLLM</a>
            <a href="#model-info-uk" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Модель</a>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class={"mx-auto px-6 sm:px-6 max-w-3xl " + proseClasses}>

        <div id="api-uk" class="not-prose mb-8 scroll-mt-[180px]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary">Hosted API</span>
            <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-slate-700"></span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted dark:text-slate-400 m-0">Звертайтеся до MamayLM через OpenAI-сумісний API — без потреби керувати інфраструктурою.</p>
          <div class="mt-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300">
            Не маєте API-ключа? <a href={apiAccessHref} class="font-semibold underline hover:text-gray-900 dark:hover:text-slate-100">Подайте запит на доступ</a> — і ключ буде надано.
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="getting-started-uk" class="!border-t-0 !mt-4 !pt-0">Початок</h2>
        <p>API MamayLM повністю сумісний із <strong>OpenAI SDK</strong>. Будь-яка бібліотека чи інструмент, що підтримує OpenAI Chat Completions API, працює з MamayLM.</p>

        <table>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td><strong>Адреса</strong></td><td><code>{apiServer}/v1</code></td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Модель</strong></td><td><code>{apiModel}</code></td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Автентифікація</strong></td><td><code>Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY</code></td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Контекст</strong></td><td>До 65 536 токенів</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Квантизація</strong></td><td>FP8 dynamic</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <p>Встановіть OpenAI Python SDK:</p>
        <Code code="pip install openai" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />

        <h2 id="chat-completions-uk">Чат</h2>

        <h3>Python</h3>
        <Code code={`from openai import OpenAI

client = OpenAI(
    base_url="${apiServer}/v1",
    api_key="YOUR_API_KEY",
)

response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="${apiModel}",
    messages=[
        {"role": "system", "content": "Ти корисний асистент."},
        {"role": "user", "content": "Поясни простими словами, як утворюється веселка."}
    ],
    max_tokens=16384,
    temperature=0.2,
)
print(response.choices[0].message.content)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>curl</h3>
        <Code code={`curl -X POST ${apiServer}/v1/chat/completions \\
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \\
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \\
  -d '{
    "model": "${apiModel}",
    "messages": [
      {"role": "user", "content": "Поясни простими словами, як утворюється веселка."}
    ],
    "max_tokens": 16384,
    "temperature": 0.2
  }'`} lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />

        <h2 id="streaming-uk">Стрімінг</h2>
        <p>Встановіть <code>stream=True</code>, щоб отримувати токени в реальному часі:</p>
        <Code code={`stream = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="${apiModel}",
    messages=[
        {"role": "user", "content": "Поясни простими словами, як утворюється веселка."}
    ],
    max_tokens=1024,
    stream=True,
)

for chunk in stream:
    delta = chunk.choices[0].delta
    if delta.content:
        print(delta.content, end="", flush=True)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h2 id="tool-calling-uk">Виклик функцій</h2>
        <p>MamayLM підтримує виклик функцій, сумісний із OpenAI. Опишіть інструменти у вигляді JSON-схем — модель сама вирішить, коли їх викликати.</p>

        <h3>1. Опис інструментів і запит</h3>
        <Code code={`tools = [
    {
        "type": "function",
        "function": {
            "name": "get_weather",
            "description": "Отримати поточну погоду для міста",
            "parameters": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "city": {"type": "string", "description": "Назва міста"},
                    "unit": {"type": "string", "enum": ["celsius", "fahrenheit"]}
                },
                "required": ["city"]
            }
        }
    }
]

response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="${apiModel}",
    messages=[
        {"role": "user", "content": "Яка погода в Києві?"}
    ],
    tools=tools,
    tool_choice="auto",
)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>2. Перевірка викликів</h3>
        <Code code={`message = response.choices[0].message

if message.tool_calls:
    for tool_call in message.tool_calls:
        print(f"Функція: {tool_call.function.name}")
        print(f"Аргументи: {tool_call.function.arguments}")
else:
    print(message.content)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>3. Надсилання результатів</h3>
        <Code code={`import json

# Після виклику вашої функції з аргументами моделі:
tool_result = {"temperature": 22, "unit": "celsius", "condition": "sunny"}

response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="${apiModel}",
    messages=[
        {"role": "user", "content": "Яка погода в Києві?"},
        message,  # повідомлення асистента з tool_calls
        {
            "role": "tool",
            "tool_call_id": message.tool_calls[0].id,
            "content": json.dumps(tool_result),
        }
    ],
    tools=tools,
)
print(response.choices[0].message.content)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <p><strong>Підтримувані значення <code>tool_choice</code>:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li><code>"auto"</code> &mdash; модель сама вирішує, чи викликати інструмент (за замовчуванням)</li>
          <li><code>"required"</code> &mdash; модель має викликати хоча б один інструмент</li>
          <li><code>"none"</code> &mdash; виклик інструментів вимкнено для цього запиту</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="vision-uk">Зображення</h2>
        <p>MamayLM v2.0 є мультимодальною та розуміє зображення. Надсилайте їх як base64 data URL.</p>

        <h3>Зображення у base64</h3>
        <Code code={`import base64

with open("photo.jpg", "rb") as f:
    b64 = base64.b64encode(f.read()).decode()

response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="${apiModel}",
    messages=[
        {
            "role": "user",
            "content": [
                {"type": "text", "text": "Опиши це зображення."},
                {
                    "type": "image_url",
                    "image_url": {"url": f"data:image/jpeg;base64,{b64}"}
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
    max_tokens=1024,
)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <div id="self-hosting-uk" class="not-prose mt-16 mb-8 scroll-mt-[180px]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary">Запустити самостійно</span>
            <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-slate-700"></span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted dark:text-slate-400 m-0">MamayLM v2.0 — відкрита модель. Запускайте 12B або 27B локально через HuggingFace Transformers або розгортайте з vLLM. API-ключ не потрібен.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 id="transformers-uk" class="!border-t-0 !mt-4 !pt-0">Запуск із HuggingFace Transformers</h2>
        <p>MamayLM v2.0 доступна на HuggingFace у розмірах <strong>27B</strong> (<a href={hfModelUrl}>{hfModel}</a>) та <strong>12B</strong> (<a href={hfModel12bUrl}>{hfModel12b}</a>). Це модель Gemma 3, тож завантажуйте її через <code>Gemma3ForConditionalGeneration</code> та <code>AutoProcessor</code>.</p>

        <Code code="pip install -U transformers accelerate torch" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>Генерація тексту</h3>
        <Code code={`from transformers import AutoProcessor, Gemma3ForConditionalGeneration
import torch

model_id = "${hfModel}"

processor = AutoProcessor.from_pretrained(model_id)
model = Gemma3ForConditionalGeneration.from_pretrained(
    model_id, device_map="auto"
).eval()

messages = [
    {
        "role": "user",
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Поясни простими словами, як утворюється веселка."}],
    },
]

inputs = processor.apply_chat_template(
    messages, add_generation_prompt=True, tokenize=True,
    return_dict=True, return_tensors="pt"
).to(model.device, dtype=torch.bfloat16)

input_len = inputs["input_ids"].shape[-1]

with torch.inference_mode():
    generation = model.generate(**inputs, max_new_tokens=512, do_sample=True, temperature=0.2)
    generation = generation[0][input_len:]

print(processor.decode(generation, skip_special_tokens=True))`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>Із зображенням</h3>
        <Code code={`messages = [
    {
        "role": "user",
        "content": [
            {"type": "image", "image": "https://huggingface.co/datasets/huggingface/documentation-images/resolve/main/bee.jpg"},
            {"type": "text", "text": "Опиши, що ти бачиш на зображенні."},
        ],
    },
]

inputs = processor.apply_chat_template(
    messages, add_generation_prompt=True, tokenize=True,
    return_dict=True, return_tensors="pt"
).to(model.device, dtype=torch.bfloat16)

input_len = inputs["input_ids"].shape[-1]

with torch.inference_mode():
    generation = model.generate(**inputs, max_new_tokens=512, do_sample=True, temperature=0.2)
    generation = generation[0][input_len:]

print(processor.decode(generation, skip_special_tokens=True))`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h2 id="vllm-uk">Запуск із vLLM</h2>
        <p>vLLM забезпечує швидкий пакетний інференс та OpenAI-сумісний сервер для локального розгортання.</p>

        <Code code="pip install vllm" lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>Python</h3>
        <Code code={`from vllm import LLM, SamplingParams

llm = LLM(model="${hfModel}")
params = SamplingParams(max_tokens=512, temperature=0.2)

messages = [
    {
        "role": "user",
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Поясни простими словами, як утворюється веселка."}],
    },
]

outputs = llm.chat(messages, sampling_params=params)
print(outputs[0].outputs[0].text)`} lang="python" theme="github-dark" />

        <h3>OpenAI-сумісний сервер</h3>
        <Code code={`vllm serve ${hfModel}`} lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />
        <p>Це піднімає OpenAI-сумісний ендпоінт на <code>http://localhost:8000/v1</code>. Звертайтеся до нього так само, як у прикладах <a href="#chat-completions-uk">Чат</a> вище — лише вкажіть туди <code>base_url</code>.</p>

        <h3>FP8 для швидшого інференсу</h3>
        <p><strong>Не</strong> використовуйте прапорець vLLM <code>quantization="fp8"</code> з базовою моделлю — він непомітно квантизує візуальну вежу та мультимодальний проєктор, що призводить до некоректних відповідей на зображення. Для зменшення пам’яті приблизно вдвічі зі збереженням зору запускайте натомість FP8 dynamic варіант:</p>
        <Code code={`vllm serve ${hfModel}-FP8-dynamic`} lang="bash" theme="github-dark" />

